{
  "stem": "25651.13",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we get to this camp in, in Gunskirchen, which is just wooden huts in the middle of a forest.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's no fence, and we're just dumped there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now and then they give us soup, and we're terribly overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The overcrowding was the worst thing, and the-- by this time the hunger and the thirst was the worst.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the, the, the roof trusses were made of timber.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were two timbers with another timber running in between.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So during the night I shimmied up into this roof truss and I slept on the roof truss.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had room to stretch out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But on the other hand, I couldn't sleep because I was afraid of falling down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you sort of sleep a half sleep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're stretched out and you're resting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I've often watched monkeys now, and I wonder how they are assured in the trees.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I felt all this time, any moment I was going to fall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, my fall would have been soft because I would have fallen on people's heads.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we, we started getting lice, everyone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were living in such close proximity to each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Yehuda Backon was there, and Misha Krause was there, various other boys.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would take our shirts off and our clothes off in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We'd have a louse hunt, and we'd kill the lice in between our thumbnails, and they make a little pop sound as you crunch them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some people were eating them because the blood, you know, you-- I mean, we didn't know about typhus and all this business.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And the thirst was worse than the hunger.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
